title: RHOC Horses & Whispers & Che Diaz

description:
Everything Iconic is back! Danny is recapping his holiday, touching on And Just Like That, the Che Diaz of it all, and then diving into The Real Housewives of Orange County, which featured a whisper scene, Shane’s ‘Pass the Bar’ party, and Terry’s chilling nighttime routine. 


RHOC Recap: 21:40ish
